WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:18.940 --> 00:00:23.420
On the occasion  of International Yoga Day a week long festival  from 16-24 June was conducted

00:00:25.540 --> 00:00:32.820
By the Indian Cultural Center SITA and the Embassy of India in Ostankino Park, Moscow

00:00:33.060 --> 00:00:38.600
And the inauguration  of the festival was done by the Ambassador of India to the Russian Federation Mr. Pankaj Saran

00:00:39.160 --> 00:00:44.140
We started celebrating the International Yoga Day in Russia from 2015

00:00:45.680 --> 00:00:56.660
This is the 4th year we are celebrating it and every year the number of participants is increasing immensely

00:00:57.560 --> 00:01:04.940
This year this festival is being celebrated in 70-80 different regions of Russia

00:01:05.120 --> 00:01:09.700
Russian people love to do Yoga

00:01:09.940 --> 00:01:12.700
and they do it on their own

00:01:12.700 --> 00:01:15.700
We are definitely trying to motivate people as much as possible

00:01:15.720 --> 00:01:24.480
But wherever I go I see people themselves are doing yoga throughout the year very excitedly and happily

00:01:24.480 --> 00:01:32.460
There is yoga teacher also in our cultural center who travels to different cities of Russia and trains people

00:01:32.480 --> 00:01:39.800
Yoga is very popular in Russia, and especially among the youth it is getting very popular

00:01:41.200 --> 00:01:47.460
There are many yoga centers in all the parts of this country

00:01:47.460 --> 00:01:52.060
People are happily doing it and are very much interested

00:01:53.140 --> 00:02:01.780
And can you please tell how actively the Russians are taking part in this year's International Yoga Day festival?

00:02:01.780 --> 00:02:08.280
This year because of the FIFA World Cup 2018 there are some restrictions

00:02:09.420 --> 00:02:14.300
But this festival which is starting today will continue for more than a week

00:02:14.620 --> 00:02:17.300
and a lot of people will be attending the program everyday

00:02:17.880 --> 00:02:20.940
there are Indian food stalls

00:02:21.520 --> 00:02:24.460
so it is a celebration of Yoga

00:02:24.460 --> 00:02:30.440
people would come, do yoga, there is our yoga teacher here and he will recite the chants

00:02:30.440 --> 00:02:35.340
there's a common yoga protocol which we will start shortly

00:02:35.340 --> 00:02:39.660
and everyday throughout the whole week there will be yoga sessions taking place over here

00:02:40.760 --> 00:02:46.980
Mr.Ambassador , please would you tell us what is the importance of yoga in your life?

00:02:48.940 --> 00:02:51.700
In my life yoga plays a very important role

00:02:51.880 --> 00:02:55.040
because I started doing yoga  ten years ago

00:02:56.360 --> 00:03:03.080
and back then I didn't know that yoga can have so much of impact

00:03:03.080 --> 00:03:09.040
not only on our physical state but also on our mental health as well

00:03:09.540 --> 00:03:18.120
And the atmosphere in which we are living we are surrounded by stress, tension and problems

00:03:18.860 --> 00:03:25.080
so for that yoga is a very appropriate and helpful system

00:03:26.640 --> 00:03:29.560
and personally it has helped me very much

00:03:29.940 --> 00:03:32.060
so that is why I always try to do Yoga

00:03:32.060 --> 00:03:36.480
So what would you like to say to our viewers on this occasion of International Yoga Day?

00:03:37.600 --> 00:03:45.020
I would say that Yoga is a gift of India to this whole world,

00:03:46.840 --> 00:03:52.900
Now I am in Russia but wherever I have been to, I have seen that Yoga is getting very popular

00:03:53.680 --> 00:03:58.980
And I wish as many people can do Yoga it's great, irrespective of their age

00:03:59.580 --> 00:04:02.920
whether they are young or old, the age doesn't matter

00:04:03.300 --> 00:04:10.840
But if you do yoga for a couple of times then I am pretty sure that  you will keep doing Yoga forever.

